      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p>This resolution calls on elected officials, faith leaders, and civil society leaders to condemn and counter acts of anti-Semitism.</p><p>The resolution also honors the contributions of Jewish-American&nbsp;servicemembers and&nbsp;commits to ensuring all Americans, including Jewish Americans, can worship without fear of violence or persecution.</p>",
